snippet.title: Alex Kidd in Pico World - playthrough
snippet.description: This is my "de-make" of Alex Kidd in Miracle World, the SEGA Master System game.  It's 100% made in Pico-8 and all it's limitations!  You can read more about it at my site - www.domariusgames.com
